<h3 data-section-id="1uo949q" data-start="1012" data-end="1034">🎯 What this does:</h3>
<ul data-start="1035" data-end="1184">
<li data-section-id="1884tpj" data-start="1035" data-end="1087">
<p data-start="1037" data-end="1087">Keeps image <strong data-start="1049" data-end="1087">centered horizontally &amp; vertically</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1avoxqo" data-start="1088" data-end="1128">
<p data-start="1090" data-end="1128">Prevents awkward cropping from edges</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="fw68wa" data-start="1129" data-end="1184">
<p data-start="1131" data-end="1184">Makes all team cards look <strong data-start="1157" data-end="1184">balanced &amp; professional</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
